name: ModMail
install_msg:
Thank you for installing the ModMail cog!
Use `[p]help ModMail` to get the list of commands and their descriptions. This cog helps manage modmail threads for your server.
If you want to help translate, go to my [crowdin](https://crowdin.com/project/Star-Cogs)
If you like my work, [donate me!](https://ko-fi.com/starcogs)
description: This cog allows you to manage modmail threads efficiently, providing tools for communication between users and moderators.
